ind or being replaced on the roster while he is not eligible to play.\\n<\\/p>\\n<p>All in all, the previous transfer rules were restrictive and created more issues for athletes than they solved. Progress has been made with the abolition of that rule. However, this leaves a generation of athletes unsure how to navigate the new system. Vixory exists to bridge the gap.<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3>Step Up With Vixory <\\/h3>\\n<p>With the ability to begin playing as soon as the transfer is complete, each athlete faces more pressure than ever to ensure they make the right choice. By using Vixory, each athlete has access to their testimonials, current statistics, coaches\\u2019 record, and so much more. All of these things serve to put the power in the hands of the player, not only to make an educated decision, but to potentially leverage a better scholarship or offer.<\\/p>\\n<p>Don\\u2019t enter into such a high stakes process blindly. Do research through a reputable source and take the future of your athletic career into your own hands. With Vixory, you can be confident that you are getting the most up to date information and most unbiased advice. Don\\u2019t play games with your eligibility.<\\/p>\",\"blog_category_id\":2,\"meta_title\":\"Using Vixory\\u2019s Resources to Your Advantage for Transferring\",\"meta_description\":\"Level the playing field when it comes to making an athletic transfer with Vixory, the tool designed for athletes.\",\"featured_image\":\"2h3Yf6STgVDqr13ivSKh4MU6Ypr4C62J3xPAEqCJ.jpg\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-07-29T00:17:29.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-07-29T00:17:29.000000Z\",\"id\":3}'),(113,'94059ccb-8d19-48d6-9f4a-e885dbf8c23b',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'','finished','','2021-07-29 00:24:23','2021-07-29 00:24:23','[]','[]'),(114,'94059cf5-7f5f-44b4-b97c-764b81bcae78',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',2,'','finished','','2021-07-29 00:24:5