"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Maintain Realistic Expectations For Yourself<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Required weekly exercise quotas to maintain strength and endurance fill the time of a student athlete, along with additional team involvement and academic progress.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">An important mentality to keep when entering into the arena of college athletics is the mentality of resilience and realistic expectations. Simply put, as you are adjusting it&rsquo;s important not to get ahead of yourself and the moment.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">It is extremely exciting to begin the journey of transfer, and to begin at a new school with a new team. However, it&#39;s important to take each day as it comes.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">First focus on learning your daily routine and setting your weekly schedule with balancing academics and athletics. Then focus on adding in time for yourself as you find that balance.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Add in social time to spend with new found friends and calling family members as well. However, remember that each day is unique and if you need to sparse your expectations for extracurriculars throughout the week, that is okay.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Becoming a student athlete is a fulltime job, so it&rsquo;s important to&nbsp; understand that the entire journey is a learning process.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:13pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Start The Day With Simple Goals<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">One way to manage your expectations&nbsp; appropriately is to begin each day with the simple goals of:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"list-style-type:disc\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Personal Hygiene<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"list-style-type:disc\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Practice<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"list-style-type:disc\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Performance<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"list-style-type:disc\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Productivity in school work<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Learning how these different bullet points interact with each other throughout the day is perfectly okay, but it&rsquo;s important to visit each of them to stay on track.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:13pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Media Management&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Streaming services, smart phones, and gaming are amazing outlets for entertainment and personal expression. However, too much screen time not only affects focusing abilities, but can also interfere with sleep.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Stimulating the brain just before bed can result in sleep coming later than intended which can affect your performance. It&rsquo;s important to keep your media time managed within earlier hours of the day, or unplugging about an hour before bed to allow your mind and body to relax from the stimulation of consuming.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Schedule Management&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">A busy person&rsquo;s path to peace is in schedule management. Learning what consistent timeblocks you are working with for finishing schoolwork, taking personal time, and performing while in uniform is the ultimate method for maintaining the expectations you, and others, have set for yourself.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montser