9,'','finished','','2021-11-08 22:33:15','2021-11-08 22:33:15','{\"is_featured\":0}','{\"is_featured\":false}'),(141,'94da091d-0a2c-4e8d-b62b-23455cfb0302',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'','finished','','2021-11-11 14:42:46','2021-11-11 14:42:46','{\"is_featured\":0}','{\"is_featured\":true}'),(142,'94da096a-80ea-4998-9150-4160c7a6e214',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'','finished','','2021-11-11 14:43:37','2021-11-11 14:43:37','{\"title\":\"When Is The Best Time for A College Transfer? Vixory Answers\",\"is_featured\":1}','{\"title\":\"When Is The Best Time for A College Transfer Vixory Answers\",\"is_featured\":false}'),(143,'94da0985-6e56-4aca-9f6f-89ff69b5a075',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',9,'','finished','','2021-11-11 14:43:55','2021-11-11 14:43:55','{\"title\":\"When Is The Best Time for A College Transfer Vixory Answers\",\"is_featured\":0}','{\"title\":\"When Is The Best Time for A College Transfer? Vixory Answers\",\"is_featured\":false}'),(144,'94f04f04-3516-465c-aaf1-16d672dda50b',2,'Delete','App\\User',128,'App\\User',128,'App\\User',128,'','finished','','2021-11-22 16:26:27','2021-11-22 16:26:27',NULL,NULL),(145,'94f04f0d-e9ab-4f5e-904e-22c52332edf0',2,'Delete','App\\User',127,'App\\User',127,'App\\User',127,'','finished','','2021-11-22 16:26:33','2021-11-22 16:26:33',NULL,NULL),(146,'94f04f17-50bf-4b77-afec-d08ab0937381',2,'Delete','App\\User',126,'App\\User',126,'App\\User',126,'','finished','','2021-11-22 16:26:39','2021-11-22 16:26:39',NULL,NULL),(147,'9518662d-666a-4357-a355-c4b8b49da3e2',1,'Create','App\\Models\\BlogPost',11,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',11,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',11,'','finished','','2021-12-12 14:44:20','2021-12-12 14:44:20',NULL,'{\"title\":\"Vixory Offers Off-Season Conditioning Tips\",\"short_description\":\"In today\\u2019s blog, Vixory will offer advice on off-season conditioning to stay in shape for the upcoming season.\",\"is_featured\":false,\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">On season routines are given, because of the mutual support coaches and teammates offer to student athletes to keep them fit and active.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Sleep, Eat Healthily, Drink Water<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">This one feels obvious, but properly caring for your body as a student-athlete is extremely important. Many young athletes forget to sleep full nights, and eat poorly because they feel they&rsquo;re invincible.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">If you are serious about becoming a career athlete, then prioritizing food that nourishes your body and resting should be your top priority.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Warm-Ups &amp; Cool-Downs<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">To avoid tearing ligaments or overstretching muscles it&rsquo;s important to remember to do your warm-ups and cool-downs.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Get into a flow of doing a 2-minute stretch with a mile to warm up your muscles, and some yoga stretches to finish the workout.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Your body will thank you for remembering to trigger some relaxation within your muscles.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Strength &amp; Cardio Balance<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Finding a balance between workouts that grow your muscles, and workouts that promote cardio and endurance is hard.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Some young athletes prefer to simply do the one they like best. However, to build proper endurance and flexibility it&rsquo;s important to find a balance between cardio and strength training.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Alternating workouts, or engaging in HIIT between weights is a great way to find that balance. You don&rsquo;t spend a ton of time on one or the other, and you achieve your desired results.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Make Time For Mental Health<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">It&rsquo;s so important to remember that your mental health is your biggest asset as a student-athlete. Your mindset is what will set you apart from other athletes.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Exercising your mental endurance is just as important as your physical endurance. So establishing mental boundaries, and mental support the same way you do for physical workouts is key.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Take advantage of your onsite counseling services, even in off-season--the door to the counseling office is open. Open up with your friends and ask for help if you feel down. Call your family.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">All of these small acts of personal service will help you build mental endurance as you balance school with athletics.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Register For Vixory Today!<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">At Vixory we care about student athletes and will work to provide as smooth a transfer process as possible. If you&rsquo;re a transferring student-athlete, or simply want to keep up with the community, sign up with us today! We&rsquo;re looking forward to connecting with you!<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"blog_category_id\":2,\"meta_title\":\"Vixory Offers Off-Season Conditioning Tips\",\"meta_description\":\"In today\\u2019s blog, Vixory will offer advice on off-season conditioning to stay in shape for the upcoming season.\",\"featured_image\":\"jI1Th2MQA66lfYqe47fDA6kVNQ8AIm7vWUOBALvc.jpg\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-12-12T14:44:20.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-12-12T14:44:20.000000Z\",\"id\":11}'),(148,'9518697e-c1c1-432b-aec2-6321aadeed33',1,'Create','App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'','finished','','2021-12-12 14:53:36','2021-12-12 14:53:36',NULL,'{\"title\":\"Can Vixory Help With College Registration?\",\"short_description\":\"In today\\u2019s blog, Vixory will offer some tips on college registration and how to best prepare.\",\"is_featured\":false,\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">The college registration process is full of minute details that are easily missed. Vixory understands this and works hard to alleviate the transition from high school to college athletics for athletes seeking to register for college. In today&rsquo;s blog, our team at Vixory offers some key tips to remember when preparing for college registration as a student-athlete.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Don&rsquo;t Procrastinate<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">It&rsquo;s important to just get started. That&rsquo;s often the hardest part of the registration process: picking a school and going for it.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">The sooner you decide to begin pinpointing a school, or group of schools, you can begin reaching out about registering as a student-athlete.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Don&rsquo;t Forget Your Resume<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Even student athletes have to submit resumes when going to college. In fact, the student-athlete college application process is often more in depth than a traditional academic student process.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Student-athletes are expected to submit resumes and portfolios of their high school stats, letters of recommendation from coaches or teachers, and your high school experience.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">It is also important to start the process of reaching out to coaches <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><em>before<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"> the registration period begins, so they have time to respond. Never pursue only one option. Always have a few open to you until you sign for one school specifically.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">If you make it known you are interviewing openly, it&#39;ll make the school most interested in you want to sign you faster. This ensures your place on the team, scholarship options, and allows you to begin your next step.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Contact The Registrar Office<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">It is important to get in touch with both your future school coach, but also the registrar office of your future college.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">The registrar&rsquo;s office will review all of your information to make sure your transcripts are received, your FAFSA is on file, your athlete paperwork is processed, and scholarships are lined up.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">You don&rsquo;t want to miss out on an incredible opportunity due to missing a small detail. The registrar&rsquo;s office can help.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Sign Up For Vixory<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Is this school only a stop along the way for you? Are you aiming for Division 1 athletics or a transfer from community college to a university? Vixory can help athletes of all journeys, and we look forward to it! Sign up with Vixory today, and we can begin the connection process to begin your athletic career.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"blog_category_id\":3,\"meta_title\":\"Can Vixory Help With College Registration?\",\"meta_description\":\"In today\\u2019s blog, Vixory will offer some tips on college registration and how to best prepare.\",\"featured_image\":\"oRMppRcJgN32loUKhdcEyEcjxo00akydqqvpMgxR.jpg\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-12-12T14:53:36.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-12-12T14:53:36.000000Z\",\"id\":12}'),(149,'95186996-7263-4ec0-8f74-c797aa4255d7',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',12,'','finished','','2021-12-12 14:53:52','2021-12-12 14:53:52','{\"is_featured\":0}','{\"is_featured\":false}'),(150,'954a04ff-0371-485a-9a2b-5355fc877f78',1,'Create','App\\Models\\BlogPost',13,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',13,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',13,'','finished','','2022-01-06 06:43:59','2022-01-06 06:43:59',NULL,'{\"title\":\"Best Places For Winter Gear Discounts By Vixory\",\"short_description\":\"In today\\u2019s blog, Vixory will offer advice on the best places to find winter gear discounts.\",\"is_featured\":false,\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Preparing for the next season is about more than training and eating well. Student- athletes must be sure they have the proper gear to head into off-season workouts or on-season games. Vixory understands this need, and the fact that student-athletes are on a budget. This is why we&rsquo;ve assembled our team to talk about the deals you can find for athletic wear and winter gear in today&rsquo;s blog.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Online Retailers<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">The majority of retailers spend money on shipping products to locations, which causes the need for markup of items being sold. Online retailers are unique in that they can utilize a network of online ordering to ship your product directly from the factory it is being made within.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Eliminating the unnecessary step of shipping to the store first causes your product to be made and shipped at cost. This is why it is often more affordable to shop online versus in the store. When it comes to athletic wear, savings where it counts always matter. Our recommendation from Vixory includes utilizing online retailers for overstock and sale items such as Amazon, 6pm, Overstock, Thread, and Zulily to get started.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Outlet Malls<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\">Online overstock retailers might provide convenience and a great deal, but there is also something to be said about utilizing your resources in the area around you. With supply chain jams resulting from the Covid-19 Pandemic continuance, it can be hard to find items in stock online. The next best alternative is to find an outlet mall near you!<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\