mart phone, or invest in a management service app, it&rsquo;s important to find the method most usable to you.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"color:#ffffff\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Join Vixory Today&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"color:#ffffff\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Vixory is here to connect student athletes with college recruiters and coaches that will lead them toward their future career. We care about our student athletes that register with us, and work to provide them an optimal experience. If you are interested in athletic transfer, we&rsquo;d love to hear from you! Follow our link to <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vixory.com\\/registration\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#ffffff\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><u>register today.&nbsp;<\\/u><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":false}'),(157,'95618f30-da41-4026-ab77-ecc3581095b0',1,'Update','App\\Models\\BlogPost',7,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',7,'App\\Models\\BlogPost',7,'','finished','','2022-01-17 23:34:27','2022-01-17 23:34:27','{\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">The professional sporting industry is filled with hopeful future professionals. Vixory is here to ensure those that utilize our service to transfer into schools that prepare them for their futures are prepared to take on that challenge. In today&rsquo;s blog, we&rsquo;ll discuss our top tips for keeping your grades in check while preparing for college transfer.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Set Aside Time For Study\\/Work Review<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">One of the priorities of every student athlete should be setting aside homework time to help manage their grades. Many student athletes go to college on sport scholarships, and these scholarships are often paired with grade requirements that must be met to keep them on the team.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Ignoring your grades is ignoring your future. So how do you manage that pressure along with the expectations as an athlete?&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">You advocate for it. Don&rsquo;t go out with friends after practice, set time aside in your schedule that is specifically designed for homework time. Then stick to that time.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Utilize Your Current School&rsquo;s Student Resources<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">&nbsp;All schools offer tutoring services, class assistance, and some form of teaching aid per subject matter focus to aid all students learning the material. If you are struggling with a particular subject, and you are a student athlete, reach out to your student resource center.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Many tutors are willing to work with tight schedules by offering virtual tutoring services, virtual work review, and personalized tutoring to the schedule that works best for you. Oftentimes specific universities will also have tutors designated to students with specific needs, such as student athletes.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Talk to your coach and teammates first to see if there is a tutor that is popularly recommended, or even designated to your team. Then follow up with your student resource center for hours available to help you succeed.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Schedule Management<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Part of the college experience is learning the meaning of the word, &lsquo;balance&rsquo;.&nbsp; Finding balance in college is about understanding priorities and how to manage them.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Schedule management is key when learning how to manage multiple priorities at once. Smart phones offer both calendar services, and scheduling task tools to keep you on track throughout your day.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">For some individuals this means color blocking out their calendar and setting hourly reminders of their tasks needing to be completed. For others it means starting each day with a To Do List of tasks to complete by the end of the day.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\">Whatever you find that works for you is awesome! Just remember to balance your academic, athletic, and emotional priorities by also allowing time for a bit of self care as well. Use your 