ed','','2022-01-17 23:34:46','2022-01-17 23:34:46','{\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#0e101a\\\">Transferring is a tricky step for student-athletes. Finding the right school is significant to a successful academic experience and, more importantly, a career in professional sports. According to the <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/nscresearchcenter.org\\/signaturereport9\\/\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#4a6ee0\\\"><u>National Student Clearinghouse Research Center<\\/u><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#0e101a\\\"> report, 37 percent of college athletes change schools at least once within their 4 to 6-year university term. If you are a student-athlete looking to transfer to a different school, today&#39;s blog, <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vixory.com\\/\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#4a6ee0\\\"><u>Vixory<\\/u><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#0e101a\\\">, explains the athletic transfer process.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-size:17pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#0e101a\\\">Determine Which School Is Right For You<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#0e101a\\\">The first step in the athletic transfer process is determining which school is 