INSERT INTO `blog_posts` VALUES (1,'What NCAA Transfer Rule Changes Mean for You',1,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">As an athlete, you will operate with the NCAA in mind. From the moment you begin the recruitment process, you will adhere to the rules and regulations they&rsquo;ve set to make the process as smooth and as fair as possible. Vixory explains how this affects you immediately.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">New Rules</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">For students who are already collegiate athletes, you will face another set of regulations should you decide to transfer programs. Fortunately for athletes everywhere, a recent rule change by the NCAA has made the process much more favorable. Beginning the 2021-2022 season, all athletes will no longer be required to sit out for an entire season following their transfer.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">This is across all sports.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Equitable Choices for You</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">One of the most infamous rules of the NCAA is the one prohibiting players to participate in the season immediately following their transfer. This has been a determining factor in many transfers, or lack thereof. The reversal of this rule has massive implications on your options as an athlete.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The main argument for this is to have equal opportunity between athletes. Previously, a volleyball player could transfer schools and play immediately, whereas a football player would have to sit out a year. This was originally implemented to deter higher profile players from transferring, but that has been determined to be inequitable, as it does not apply to athletes across the board.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Ultimately, this grants you as an athlete the autonomy to make decisions that best suit your athletic and academic career without the hindrance of a lost year.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Let Vixory Help</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Vixory accommodates that goal. You can showcase your talents to your future coach, get in touch with a college recruiter, and do so without your current coach having access to your Vixory file.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"/registration\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Register today and take Vixory for a spin. It doesn&rsquo;t take a lot of time, and you can upload your player stats and highlight reels.</span></a></p>','2021-07-29 00:05:00','2022-01-17 23:36:41','NCAA Transfer Rule Changes and You, a blog by Vixory','Vixory gives the inside information on how to optimize the NCAA rules and use them to your advantage.',1,'3vYASCbOIaLG0v0vNlAmuAHfJDQjDtvj1ZnDQpWp.jpg','The main argument for this is to have equal opportunity between athletes. Previously, a volleyball player could transfer schools and play immediately, whereas a football player would have to sit out a year. This was originally implemented to deter higher profile players from transferring, but that has been determined to be inequitable, as it does not apply to athletes across the board.'),(2,'How Vixory Helps You to Transfer Schools',2,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">So you&rsquo;ve decided to transfer schools. Now what?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">That&rsquo;s what Vixory was created for. Our goal is to assist athletes in their decision and throughout the process of transferring schools under the NCAA. The process is archaic at best, and for modern day student-athletes, the process should be both seamless and painless.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Stand Out From the Crowd</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">With so many factors ranging from athletic programs to academics to financial circumstances, the decision between schools is far from simple. Vixory allows both players and coaches/scouts to represent themselves how they see fit. Both parties benefit from our eligibility confirmation requirements, which state that a player must show proof of their compliance with the standards of their athletic affiliation (NCAA, NAIA, NJCAA).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Upload Your Stats</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Our player profiles allow you to include the statistics and highlights you choose, and exclude any you don&rsquo;t want shown. Upload highlight reels, accolades, articles, and statistics to attract potential future coaches. Your athletic resume will not be available to your current institution, which eliminates concern for athletes who have not yet made their transfer official.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Deep Dive</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">As an athlete, it can be difficult to assess a school from a visit alone. Vixory features player videos, articles on the team, program and coach, and a full statistical database.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">You are able to do in-depth research on both parties at any point in the transfer process. The information featured on our platform is exclusive to our members alone, giving Vixory athletes yet another advantage over their peers. If a coach is interested in communicating further, they have the ability to send a communication request to you, which you may choose whether or not to accept.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Register Today for Vixory</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">As you begin a quickly changing and highly competitive process, you want all available resources at your fingertips. If you are an athlete considering entering the transfer portal, you need Vixory on your team. </span><a href=\"/registration\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Register today</span></a><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">!</span></p>','2021-07-29 00:13:58','2022-01-17 23:36:25','Using Vixorys Resources to Your Advantage to Transfer Schools','The technology and expertise used at Vixory gives athletes a huge advantage when it comes to transferring schools successfully.',0,'s9iX4Z8KB2i94TWnGbo0KawW9m7ozytthuSlvoAE.jpg','Our goal is to assist athletes in their decision and throughout the process of transferring schools under the NCAA. The process is archaic at best, and for modern day student-athletes, the process should be both seamless and painless.'),(3,'How to Use Vixory\'s Resources to Your Advantage',2,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">College is overwhelming. Athletics are overwhelming. Transferring to a new school with a new athletic program and navigating all of the details is on another level. Luckily for college athletes everywhere, Vixory was created for that very reason.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Transferring Schools Just Got Easier</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The governing bodies such as the NCAA, NAIA, and NJCAA have ever-changing rules and regulations dictating each process involved in collegiate athletics. One of the most heavily regulated functions is the act of transferring from one program to another.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Previously, if an athlete who sought to transfer to another institution would have to sit out for a year. Not only does this impact their skill level as a player by benching them for an entire year, but it costs them recruiting opportunities during a season.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">For example, if a sophomore quarterback wanted to transfer colleges, he would have to sit out his entire junior year and possibly stay in school for a fifth year. This would cost him playing time in front of NFL scouts during one of the most crucial years of his recruiting career. Not to mention, he runs the risk of falling behind or being replaced on the roster while he is not eligible to play.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">All in all, the previous transfer rules were restrictive and created more issues for athletes than they solved. Progress has been made with the abolition of that rule. However, this leaves a generation of athletes unsure how to navigate the new system. Vixory exists to bridge the gap.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Step Up With Vixory</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">With the ability to begin playing as soon as the transfer is complete, each athlete faces more pressure than ever to ensure they make the right choice. By using Vixory, each athlete has access to their testimonials, current statistics, coaches&rsquo; record, and so much more. All of these things serve to put the power in the hands of the player, not only to make an educated decision, but to potentially leverage a better scholarship or offer.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Don&rsquo;t enter into such a high stakes process blindly. Do research through a reputable source and take the future of your athletic career into your own hands. With Vixory, you can be confident that you are getting the most up to date information and most unbiased advice. Don&rsquo;t play games with your eligibility.</span></p>','2021-07-29 00:17:29','2022-01-17 23:36:06','Using Vixorys Resources to Your Advantage for Transferring','Level the playing field when it comes to making an athletic transfer with Vixory, the tool designed for athletes.',1,'2h3Yf6STgVDqr13ivSKh4MU6Ypr4C62J3xPAEqCJ.jpg','The governing bodies such as the NCAA, NAIA, and NJCAA have ever-changing rules and regulations dictating each process involved in collegiate athletics. One of the most heavily regulated functions is the act of transferring from one program to another.'),(4,'Statistics about Student-Athlete College Transfers',2,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">University placement is a pivotal moment in a young athlete&#39;s life. College transfers are among the highest in the nation, especially for student-athletes. In today&#39;s blog by Vixory, we highlight essential statistics on student-athlete transfers and ways transferring schools will benefit your game and your potential career.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Basketball Student-Athlete Transfers</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">There is no question that basketball is one of the most popular sports in the world, totaling more than 18,000 National Collegiate Athletic Association (NCAA) Participants.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The Athletics Directory (ADU) reports basketball college transfers are the second highest in the organization with a 33% transfer rate. That means for every three players in the league, at least one will transfer. Student-Athlete transfers are crucial since transitioning out other players for newer or more skilled ones could mean the difference between more wins than losses for a season.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">College Transfer Common Facts</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Numbers show that 40% of all college transfers receive academic funding, leave school, or fail to graduate within a 6-year timeframe.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Vixory cares about the well-being of all student-athletes. Through our connective and school matching programs, we align students with the proper coaches and programs designed to elevate their game and increase the odds of success in all areas of sports, academics, and personal development.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Divisions Matter</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The skills that a student-athlete exemplifies determine what divisions suit their repertoire. Divisional placement directly reflects the caliber of an athlete&#39;s abilities and the level of success they will contribute to their particular team or industry.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Division 1 players are more in-demand and viewed as the most prestigious players. Division 2 offers scholarships on a smaller scale than D1, and the sporting departments usually do not have access to the same level of funding.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Statistics show college transfers are significantly higher for Division 2 teams than Division 1. At least 18% of D2 students transfer from a different college compared to 13% for D1 students. This transfer rate is slightly higher amongst men than women.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Regardless of which division you lie in, hard work overpowers rank ten-fold. Accelerate your game and increase your repertoire through Vixory.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">We showcase talented college players like yourself to gain recognition amongst coaches and scouts. At Vixory, we will not let your hard work and efforts go unrecognized. Check out our frequently asked questions page to get more information on Vixory.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Let Vixory Help Your Future Career</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Whether it is to play professionally or being a part of a team that cares, your college career is in the right hands via our placement and matching profiles at Vixory. After creating your personalized portfolio, add stats, highlights, articles, and more, showcasing your talents and why college universities need you today.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Why wait? Start the registration process and learn more about why Vixory is the perfect platform for you.</span></p>','2021-07-29 00:54:16','2022-01-17 23:35:39','Student-Athlete College Transfer Statistics, Vixory','Vixory helps students-athletes get the recognition they deserve, read about common college transfer statistics today.',0,'SY1pL52DiaNcMBno4aEMN7CfG8DxHVpqCvg5idSN.jpg','University placement is a pivotal moment in a young athlete\'s life. College transfers are among the highest in the nation, especially for student-athletes. \r\nIn today\'s blog by Vixory, we highlight essential statistics on student-athlete transfers and ways transferring schools will benefit your game and your potential career.'),(5,'Vixorys Quick Guide on How Rapsodo, Blast, and Trackman Work to Improve Your Skills',3,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Sporting technology is changing the way athletes learn and hone their skills on the road to professionalism. There are multiple advantages to investing in these revolutionary devices and applications. In today&rsquo;s blog by Vixory, we list our three favorite performance assessment apps and how using them will improve your life and game skills.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">How Rapsodo Benefits Sports Athletes.</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Rapsodo is the leader of sports analytics and assessment technology. Mainly used in baseball, Rapsodo is an application that works to integrate and deliver reports simultaneously with performance measurement devices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">At Vixory, we are big fans of integrative technology such as Rapsodo to help athletes reach their max potential and more. Rapsodo accelerates player development using radar technology and data analysis to measure personal abilities essential to building your player skill set.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Used by most Major League Baseball (MLB) teams, this technology measures velocity, speed, angles, heights, pitching efficiency, strike degree, and more.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The days of inaccurate pitching are long gone. Rapsodo utilizes 3d modeling, spin rate tracking, and data overlay to display a slowed-down replay of your pitch, indicating areas of improvement. Baseball teams do not only use Rapsodo; golfers also benefit from The Rapsodo Mobile Launch Monitor (MLM) feature designed to deliver pro-level launching techniques all from the convenience of your smartphone device.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">The golfing active shot tracker supplies player&rsquo;s with the tools and accessories to refine their game. Ideal for indoor/outdoor use, Rapsodo comes equipped with pitch tunneling coaching, immediate video feedback, and easy-to-navigate app features. Speak to the professionals at Vixory about Rapsodo and its coaching features.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Develop Your Golf Swing With Trackman</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Frequently used by golfers, Trackman differs from its competitors from its dual radar tracking and 3D imaging designed to portray club to ball driving range and impact zones.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">No other launch pad technology comes equipped with these high-definition features making Trackman an essential tool for improving a player&rsquo;s aptitude. Trackman can measure a golf drive up to half a millisecond and guarantees precise monitoring at the exact moment of impact, eliminating any potential data errors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Increase Your Batting Average Through Blast Technology</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Blast motion is a measurement software application developed for reporting, swing consistency, execution scores, impact position, and power drives related to hitting accuracy and body rotations.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Blast Motion uses reader insights to align your target goals, making it the only technology in its class to curate high-level performance players. Coupled with the first-ever manufactured &ldquo;Smart Bat,&rdquo; Blast Motion&rsquo;s integrative features work in unison with the Smart Bat to deliver swing metrics and hit regularity reports.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">It is known as the industry&rsquo;s most precise swing analyzer supplemented with coaching assessments, player insights, and more. Use Blast Motion to capture pivotal moments in your game and upload it to your Vixory profile.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Join Vixory Today</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">Vixory recommends the connective and assessment features of sporting technology to strengthen your game, especially during solo training days. Highlight special moments, showcase daily improvement reports, and more, all available under your personal player&rsquo;s profile. With the help of Vixory and techs like Rapsodo and Trackman, players will never have to worry about dropping the ball. Visit the Vixory website and register today.</span></p>','2021-07-29 01:00:17','2022-01-17 23:35:05','How to Improve Skills With Rapsodo, Blast, and Trackman | Vixory','Presented by Vixory, dive into this quick guide on the benefits of skill enhancing technology for professional and starting athletes.',0,'ZcYlsgPMpLpAjwe2d6XMNNR8Kp2QIqS35g3e82rD.jpg','Sporting technology is changing the way athletes learn and hone their skills on the road to professionalism. There are multiple advantages to investing in these revolutionary devices and applications. In todays blog by Vixory, we list our three favorite performance assessment apps and how using them will improve your life and game skills.'),(6,'Steps To Take To Begin The Athletic Transfer Process, Vixory Explains',2,'<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">Transferring is a tricky step for student-athletes. Finding the right school is significant to a successful academic experience and, more importantly, a career in professional sports. According to the </span></span></span><a href=\"https://nscresearchcenter.org/signaturereport9/\" style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\"><u>National Student Clearinghouse Research Center</u></span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\"> report, 37 percent of college athletes change schools at least once within their 4 to 6-year university term. If you are a student-athlete looking to transfer to a different school, today&#39;s blog, </span></span></span><a href=\"https://vixory.com/\" style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\"><u>Vixory</u></span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">, explains the athletic transfer process.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:17pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">Determine Which School Is Right For You</span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">The first step in the athletic transfer process is determining which school is right for you. Some beneficial aspects to look at before choosing are program success rates, FIis it a Division 1 or Division 2 school, program or scholarship eligibility, and academic criteria. Student-athletes must ensure they can develop and enhance their sports abilities and accelerate their academic success.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:17pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">Show Your Interest&nbsp;</span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif\">Demonstrate interest in your institution by reaching out