INSERT INTO `frequently_asked_questions` VALUES (1,'Why do I need to register?','A coach must register for Vixory to be able to search for potential transfer college athletes based on the specific needs of your team. We make it easy and accessible for you to find a list of athletes who want to transfer to a school like yours.\r\nAthletes must register to allow their information to be searched and accessed by coaches.','2020-10-28 19:10:30','2020-12-15 19:16:44'),(2,'How do I search for an athlete?','Once you are registered, you can choose the criteria for the particular needs of your team. You can make a broad search or narrow it down as much as you choose. We recommend that your initial search be as broad as possible then narrow it down.','2020-10-28 19:10:30','2020-10-28 19:10:30'),(3,'How do I contact an athlete?','If you find an athlete who you are interested in talking to, request to connect with the athlete. The athlete must accept your request in order for you to receive their contact information. If an athlete does not accept your request, please do not send additional requests to them.  All communication is done outside of Vixory after the initial contact, through the coach and athlete\'s email or telephone number.  We do not track any communications between coaches and athletes.','2020-10-28 19:10:30','2020-12-15 19:15:16'),(4,'Will a coach be able to see athletes from their school on the site?','No, the site is designed so that coaches may only see athletes from other schools that want to transfer.','2020-10-28 19:10:30','2020-12-15 19:13:00'),(5,'Is the athletes inclusion in Vixory confirmation that the athlete can transfer?','We require the athlete to confirm that he or she is eligible to transfer and is in compliance with the requirements of their current affiliation, whether it is the NCAA, NAIA, NJCAA, etc. We do not make any independent investigation of the athletes compliance.','2020-10-28 19:10:30','2020-12-15 19:11:55'),(6,'What is the Connections section on my page?','It is a list of the coaches or athletes that you have made contact with so that you can follow up and reach out to them.  After you make a Connection in Vixory you will need to communicate through your personal phone or email.  We do not track any communication and want to protect your privacy by giving you control of your communications.','2020-11-17 16:58:45','2020-11-17 16:58:45');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `frequently_asked_questions` ENABLE KEYS */;
